Root-cause classification:

```text
data_generation = not_primary_blocker
probe_infrastructure = working
representation_training = not_first_decisive_failure
mdn_loss_optimization = working_by_loss
mdn_policy_relevant_signal = failing
policy_training = downstream_of_failed_forecast_gate
