Next diagnostic target:

```text
Inspect why MDN loss improvement does not improve edge-return sign/rank:
target scaling, target feature weighting, MDN objective alignment, close-return
projection semantics, representation phase readout, and simple supervised
oracle/baseline comparisons before PPO tuning.
```

